<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Strenos Support</title>
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; --bg: #fff; --fg: #1a1a1a; --muted: #6e6e73; --accent: #007aff; --border: #e5e5ea; --code-bg: #f5f5f7; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { :root { --bg: #000; --fg: #f5f5f7; --muted: #98989d; --accent: #0a84ff; --border: #38383a; --code-bg: #1c1c1e; } }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 56px 24px 80px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--fg); background: var(--bg); }
    h1 { font-size: 36px; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .subtitle { color: var(--muted); font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 40px; }
    h2 { font-size: 22px; margin: 40px 0 16px; }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
    .contact { background: var(--code-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0 32px; }
    .contact strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .contact .note { margin: 12px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    dt { font-weight: 600; margin: 24px 0 8px; font-size: 17px; }
    dd { margin: 0 0 12px; }
    footer { margin-top: 64px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    footer a { color: var(--muted); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Strenos Support</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Help, FAQ, and contact for the Strenos workout tracker.</p>

  <div class="contact">
    <strong>Email</strong>
    <a href="mailto:strenos.support@gmail.com">strenos.support@gmail.com</a>
    <p class="note">We typically respond within 24&ndash;48 hours.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <dl>
    <dt>How do I restore my purchases on a new device?</dt>
    <dd>Open Strenos &rarr; Settings &rarr; Restore Purchases. Make sure you&rsquo;re signed into the same Apple ID used for the original purchase.</dd>

    <dt>How do I cancel my subscription?</dt>
    <dd>Settings &rarr; Manage Subscription opens Apple&rsquo;s native subscription manager. The subscription stays active until the end of the current period after cancellation.</dd>

    <dt>Where is my workout data stored?</dt>
    <dd>In your private iCloud database, encrypted by Apple. Strenos has no servers and does not share your data. See our <a href="https://artyomsbr.github.io/strenos-privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</dd>

    <dt>I bought Lifetime &mdash; why is it not showing as Active?</dt>
    <dd>Tap Restore Purchases. If still missing, confirm you&rsquo;re on the same Apple ID and have internet access.</dd>

    <dt>Apple Health data isn&rsquo;t syncing.</dt>
    <dd>iOS Settings &rarr; Privacy &amp; Security &rarr; Health &rarr; Strenos &rarr; enable Heart Rate, Active Energy, and Workouts.</dd>

    <dt>Can I use Strenos without an account?</dt>
    <dd>Yes. Strenos works fully offline on a single device. Sign in with Apple is optional and only enables cross-device sync via iCloud.</dd>

    <dt>How do I delete my account and data?</dt>
    <dd>Settings &rarr; Delete Account. This removes your local profile and clears your iCloud data. The action is permanent.</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>Found a bug?</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:strenos.support@gmail.com">strenos.support@gmail.com</a> with iOS version, device model, and steps to reproduce. Screenshots help.</p>

  <footer>
    <a href="https://artyomsbr.github.io/strenos-privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> &middot; Strenos &copy; 2026
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
